1
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,920
Hey!

2
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:48,320
What exactly did you give Mr. Chen to drink

3
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,050
that's causing him such agony?

4
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,840
If you've done anything suspicious

5
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:53,500
and Mr. Chen comes to any harm,

6
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:56,660
I'll have your head separated from your body right now.

7
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:58,000
Where is Nongyu?

8
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,360
Master.

9
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,800
I'm here.

10
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:01,330
Mr. Chen.

11
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:02,360
Nongyu.

12
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:04,769
You truly have remarkable skills.

13
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:07,010
How are you feeling now?

14
00:01:07,240 --> 00:01:09,039
Don't you feel in your mouth,

15
00:01:09,039 --> 00:01:10,720
first bitter then astringent,

16
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:13,640
finally changing from a musky sandalwood aroma to a sweet aftertaste,

17
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,760
instantly refreshing your mind and spirit,

18
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,820
as if your head has suddenly cleared?

19
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,240
Yes, exactly.

20
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,880
My headache is actually gone.

21
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:24,680
Nongyu,

22
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,360
