31
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:54,360
I just tasted hundreds of herbs in the Western Regions years ago.

32
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:56,440
Over time, they've entered my body.

33
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:59,440
Some of them are precious herbs.

34
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,770
Rare in Central Plains.

35
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,160
