137
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:30,280
That bowl of tea leaves you despise

138
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:32,880
would be enough for a full meal for these sisters.

139
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,880
Mr. Li, as an official of the Chen household,

140
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:37,340
surely you won't let them starve and freeze.

141
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:38,680
Give me money.

142
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,770
