159
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,880
buying herbs and daily necessities in the market,

160
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:50,040
while all other hours she's seeing patients at the clinic.

161
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,560
What about the patients?

162
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:53,440
No suspicious individuals.

163
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,560
